# Versioning policy: the pinned ``version`` here must match
# ``[project] version`` in agribrain/backend/pyproject.toml. The
# tests/test_metadata_consistency.py guard fails the build if they
# drift. ``date-released`` is set to the date the v<X.Y.Z> tag is
# pushed; bump both together with the tag.
#
# Active maintenance through 2026-Q2. Cite the version + commit SHA
# from `mvp/simulation/results/artifact_manifest.json` for paper-grade
# reproducibility.
license: MIT
