# DOI placeholder. To register a DOI for this release:
#   1. Tag the commit:
#        git tag -a v1.2.0 -m "AGRI-BRAIN v1.2.0"
#        git push origin v1.2.0
#   2. Mint a Zenodo DOI by importing the GitHub repo at
#      https://zenodo.org/account/settings/github/ (one-time setup)
#      and publish the v1.2.0 release on GitHub. Zenodo will
#      auto-create a versioned DOI of the form
#        10.5281/zenodo.<NNNNNNN>
#   3. Replace the empty `doi:` value below with the minted DOI.
#   4. The README citation block reads from this file via cff-cli;
#      no other file needs editing.
